      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "# load_surveys_microdata()   -note: it is loading partitions, not og surveys\n   -load a single survey by (release, country, year, welfare_type)\n\n# load_surveys()                       -note: it is loading partitions, not og surveys\n    - batch load via a manifest data.table subset. \n    - (NOTE) Can retrieve the manifest of the release asked by the user \n                     with piptm_manifests(\"20260101_TEST\")\n",
      "fontSize": 14.338369920141687,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "# load_surveys_microdata()   -note: it is loading partitions, not og surveys\n   -load a single survey by (release, country, year, welfare_type)\n\n# load_surveys()                       -note: it is loading partitions, not og surveys\n    - batch load via a manifest data.table subset. \n    - (NOTE) Can retrieve the manifest of the release asked by the user \n                     with piptm_manifests(\"20260101_TEST\")\n",
